# Open Plex Web App
# Navigate to your Plex server's web interface by entering the following URL in your browser:
http://localhost:32400/web

# Sign in to your Plex account if prompted.

# Access Media Item
# Click on any media item (e.g., a movie or TV show episode) to open its details page.

# Retrieve XML Data
# Click the three-dot menu (â‹¯) on the media item's page.
# Select "Get Info" from the dropdown menu.
# In the information window, click the "View XML" button.

# Extract Plex Token
# The XML data will open in a new browser tab.
# In the URL of this new tab, locate the parameter 'X-Plex-Token=' followed by your token value.
# Copy the token value for your use.
